Invocation Name: digital delight
des:
Digital Delight provides smart commercial, smart home, smart kitchen & smart bath design, installation and service. 

To get started, say "Alexa, ask Digital Delight for more information."

You can ask other questions like:
...what does Digital Delight offer
...what products does Digital Delight sell
...why choose Digital Delight as your home technology provider
...what are customers saying about Digital Delight
...what are Digital Delight deals
...where can I learn more about Digital Delight.
